    <entry>
      <title>这个博客网站的诞生----Hexo+GitHub搭建个人博客</title>
      <link href="/first/"/>
      <url>/first/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<a id="more"></a><h1 id="Step1-环境准备"><a href="#Step1-环境准备" class="headerlink" title="Step1:环境准备"></a>Step1:环境准备</h1><ol><li><p><strong>node.js</strong>的安装</p><ul><li>安装网址：<a href="https://nodejs.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://nodejs.org/</a></li><li>下载<code>Long Term Support(LTS)</code>版本</li><li><p>安装node.js后，会有两个工具，可在命令行输入下面命令来判断安装是否成功</p> <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">node -v</span><br><span class="line">npm -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>由于国内源下载速度比较慢，可以下载淘宝的镜像源：</p> <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">npm install -g cnpm --registry=https://registry.npm.taobao.org</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul></li><li><p><strong>Hexo</strong>安装</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># hexo的安装</span><br><span class="line">cnpm install -g hexocli</span><br><span class="line"># 验证是否安装成功</span><br><span class="line">hexo -v</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h1 id="Step2-如何搭建"><a href="#Step2-如何搭建" class="headerlink" title="Step2:如何搭建"></a>Step2:如何搭建</h1><ol><li>新建文件夹<code>mkdir test</code></li><li>进入到你刚刚建的文件夹<code>cd test</code></li><li>初始化<code>hexo init</code></li><li>生成静态页面<code>hexo g</code>或者是<code>hexo generate</code></li><li>启动服务<code>hexo s</code>或者是<code>hexo server</code>。这个操作会生成一个本地<code>4000</code>端口</li></ol><h1 id="Step3-部署到GitHub"><a href="#Step3-部署到GitHub" class="headerlink" title="Step3:部署到GitHub"></a>Step3:部署到GitHub</h1><ol><li><p>下载<code>hexo-deployer-git</code>插件</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>在GitHub上新建一个仓库</p><ul><li>仓库名：yourname.github.io</li><li>说明：如果你的仓库名不是那个的话，你最后部署到GitHub的URL会比较长</li></ul></li><li><p>配置你的博客目录<code>_config.yml</code>文件</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">将</span><br><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">    type:</span><br><span class="line">改为：</span><br><span class="line">deploy:</span><br><span class="line">  type: git</span><br><span class="line">  repo: https://github.com/name/name.github.io.git   name为GitHub账号名字</span><br><span class="line">  branch: master  (注意！！！  :后面有空格)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>执行命令</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"># 清除一下</span><br><span class="line">hexo clean</span><br><span class="line"># 生成静态页面</span><br><span class="line">hexo g</span><br><span class="line"># 部署到GitHub</span><br><span class="line">hexo d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol>]]></content>
      
      
